## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not capture the full spectrum of reasons behind fast food's popularity. Additionally, some sources, such as Reddit, are user-generated and may not be as reliable as peer-reviewed studies. The data is also primarily focused on the US and UK, which may not reflect global trends. Further research could include a broader range of geographical locations and more diverse types of sources to provide a more comprehensive analysis.